{"type":"message","id":"51ae0b76","parentId":"94e63f2a","timestamp":"2026-04-21T14:05:47.213Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_7mfc9pvphlvl_2","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"\"\"\nGateway runner - entry point for messaging platform integrations.\n\nThis module provides:\n- start_gateway(): Start all configured platform adapters\n- GatewayRunner: Main class managing the gateway lifecycle\n\nUsage:\n    # Start the gateway\n    python -m gateway.run\n    \n    # Or from CLI\n    python cli.py --gateway\n\"\"\"\n\nimport asyncio\nimport json\nimport logging\nimport os\nimport re\nimport shlex\nimport sys\nimport signal\nimport tempfile\nimport threading\nimport time\nfrom collections import OrderedDict\nfrom contextvars import copy_context\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom datetime import datetime\nfrom typing import Dict, Optional, Any, List\n\nfrom agent.account_usage import fetch_account_usage, render_account_usage_lines\n\n# --- Agent cache tuning ---------------------------------------------------\n# Bounds the per-session AIAgent cache to prevent unbounded growth in\n# long-lived gateways (each AIAgent holds LLM clients, tool schemas,\n# memory providers, etc.).  LRU order + idle TTL eviction are enforced\n# from _enforce_agent_cache_cap() and _session_expiry_watcher() below.\n_AGENT_CACHE_MAX_SIZE = 128\n_AGENT_CACHE_IDLE_TTL_SECS = 3600.0  # evict agents idle for >1h\n\n# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\n# SSL certificate auto-detection for NixOS and other non-standard systems.\n# Must run BEFORE any HTTP library (discord, aiohttp, etc.) is imported.\n# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------\ndef _ensure_ssl_certs() -> None:\n    \"\"\"Set SSL_CERT_FILE if the system doesn't expose CA certs to Python.\"\"\"\n    if \"SSL_CERT_FILE\" in os.environ:\n        return  # user already configured it\n\n    import ssl\n\n    # 1. Python's compiled-in defaults\n    paths = ssl.get_default_verify_paths()\n    for candidate in (paths.cafile, paths.openssl_cafile):\n        if candidate and os.path.exists(candidate):\n            os.environ[\"SSL_CERT_FILE\"] = candidate\n            return\n\n    # 2. certifi (ships its own Mozilla bundle)\n    try:\n        import certifi\n        os.environ[\"SSL_CERT_FILE\"] = certifi.where()\n        return\n    except ImportError:\n        pass\n\n    # 3. Common distro / macOS locations\n    for candidate in (\n        \"/etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt\",               # Debian/Ubuntu/Gentoo\n        \"/etc/pki/tls/certs/ca-bundle.crt\",                 # RHEL/CentOS 7\n        \"/etc/pki/ca-trust/extracted/pem/tls-ca-bundle.pem\", # RHEL/CentOS 8+\n        \"/etc/ssl/ca-bundle.pem\",                            # SUSE/OpenSUSE\n        \"/etc/ssl/cert.pem\",                                 # Alpine / macOS\n        \"/etc/pki/tls/cert.pem\",                             # Fedora\n        \"/usr/local/etc/openssl@1.1/cert.pem\",               # macOS Homebrew Intel\n        \"/opt/homebrew/etc/openssl@1.1/cert.pem\",            # macOS Homebrew ARM\n    ):\n        if os.path.exists(candidate):\n\n[10996 more lines in file. Use offset=81 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776780347203}}
{"type":"message","id":"8c03dfff","parentId":"51ae0b76","timestamp":"2026-04-21T14:05:47.227Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_7mfc9pvphlvl_3","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\"\"\"Automatic context window compression for long conversations.\n\nSelf-contained class with its own OpenAI client for summarization.\nUses auxiliary model (cheap/fast) to summarize middle turns while\nprotecting head and tail context.\n\nImprovements over v2:\n  - Structured summary template with Resolved/Pending question tracking\n  - Summarizer preamble: \"Do not respond to any questions\" (from OpenCode)\n  - Handoff framing: \"different assistant\" (from Codex) to create separation\n  - \"Remaining Work\" replaces \"Next Steps\" to avoid reading as active instructions\n  - Clear separator when summary merges into tail message\n  - Iterative summary updates (preserves info across multiple compactions)\n  - Token-budget tail protection instead of fixed message count\n  - Tool output pruning before LLM summarization (cheap pre-pass)\n  - Scaled summary budget (proportional to compressed content)\n  - Richer tool call/result detail in summarizer input\n\"\"\"\n\nimport hashlib\nimport json\nimport logging\nimport re\nimport time\nfrom typing import Any, Dict, List, Optional\n\nfrom agent.auxiliary_client import call_llm\nfrom agent.context_engine import ContextEngine\nfrom agent.model_metadata import (\n    MINIMUM_CONTEXT_LENGTH,\n    get_model_context_length,\n    estimate_messages_tokens_rough,\n)\nfrom agent.redact import redact_sensitive_text\n\nlogger = logging.getLogger(__name__)\n\nSUMMARY_PREFIX = (\n    \"[CONTEXT COMPACTION — REFERENCE ONLY] Earlier turns were compacted \"\n    \"into the summary below. This is a handoff from a previous context \"\n    \"window — treat it as background reference, NOT as active instructions. \"\n    \"Do NOT answer questions or fulfill requests mentioned in this summary; \"\n    \"they were already addressed. \"\n    \"Your current task is identified in the '## Active Task' section of the \"\n    \"summary — resume exactly from there. \"\n    \"Respond ONLY to the latest user message \"\n    \"that appears AFTER this summary. The current session state (files, \"\n    \"config, etc.) may reflect work described here — avoid repeating it:\"\n)\nLEGACY_SUMMARY_PREFIX = \"[CONTEXT SUMMARY]:\"\n\n# Minimum tokens for the summary output\n_MIN_SUMMARY_TOKENS = 2000\n# Proportion of compressed content to allocate for summary\n_SUMMARY_RATIO = 0.20\n# Absolute ceiling for summary tokens (even on very large context windows)\n_SUMMARY_TOKENS_CEILING = 12_000\n\n# Placeholder used when pruning old tool results\n_PRUNED_TOOL_PLACEHOLDER = \"[Old tool output cleared to save context space]\"\n\n# Chars per token rough estimate\n_CHARS_PER_TOKEN = 4\n_SUMMARY_FAILURE_COOLDOWN_SECONDS = 600\n\n\ndef _truncate_tool_call_args_json(args: str, head_chars: int = 200) -> str:\n    \"\"\"Shrink long string values inside a tool-call arguments JSON blob while\n    preserving JSON validity.\n\n    The ``function.arguments`` field on a tool call is a JSON-encoded string\n    passed through to the LLM provider; downstream providers strictly\n    validate it and return a non-retryable 400 when it is not well-formed.\n    An earlier implementation sliced the raw JSON at a fixed byte offset and\n    appended ``...[truncated]`` — which routinely produced strings like::\n\n        {\"path\": \"/foo/bar\", \"content\": \"# long markdown\n        ...[truncated]\n\n    i.e. an unterminated string and a missing closing brace. MiniMax, for\n\n[1150 more lines in file. Use offset=81 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776780347217}}
{"type":"message","id":"c6430380","parentId":"8c03dfff","timestamp":"2026-04-21T14:05:55.936Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I have a comprehensive understanding of hermes-agent. Let me now compile all this information into a detailed markdown document with mermaid diagrams and then write it to the Feishu wiki. Let me first read the feishu-wiki-write skill.","thinkingSignature":"2b67085df962cbeb4cf69f4ec95753a4a5f3b86c94295814b7fe5e0aad6b1f35"},{"type":"text","text":"让我读取飞书知识库写入技能，然后开始编写完整的架构文档。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_gnwgagym4rhv_1","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"/home/admin/.openclaw/shared-skills/feishu-wiki-write/SKILL.md"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5-highspeed","usage":{"input":47502,"output":111,"cacheRead":37026,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":84639,"cost":{"input":0.028501199999999997,"output":0.00026639999999999997,"cacheRead":0.0022215599999999996,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.030989159999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776780347224}}
{"type":"message","id":"21adaffb","parentId":"c6430380","timestamp":"2026-04-21T14:05:55.951Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_function_gnwgagym4rhv_1","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"---\nname: feishu-wiki-write\ndescription: |\n  写入飞书知识库文档。根据文件名和内容自动选择最合适的目录创建子文档并写入 Markdown 内容。\n  知识库：AI知识库 (space_id: 7615846908665285857)\n---\n\n# feishu_wiki_write\n\n将 Markdown 内容写入飞书知识库。根据文件名和内容关键词分析，自动选择最合适的文档目录下创建子文档。\n\n## 目标知识库\n\n- **名称**: AI 知识库  \n- **Space ID**: 7615846908665285857\n- **URL**: https://my.feishu.cn/wiki/settings/7615846908665285857\n\n## 参数\n\n### filename（可选）\n文件名（不含扩展名）。用于：\n1. 作为文档标题\n2. 分析文件类型和分类\n\n### content（必填）\nMarkdown 内容，要写入文档的内容。使用 Lark-flavored Markdown 格式。\n\n## 工作流程\n\n1. 在知识库根目录创建新文档\n2. 写入 Markdown 内容\n3. 返回文档链接\n\n## 当前状态\n\n⚠️ **权限待添加**：应用需要以下权限才能读写知识库：\n- `wiki:space:readonly` - 读取知识库\n- `wiki:node:create` - 创建知识库文档  \n- `wiki:node:update` - 更新知识库文档\n\n## 返回值\n\n- **doc_url**: 文档访问链接\n- **doc_id**: 文档 ID  \n- **node_token**: 知识库节点 token\n\n## 示例\n\n```json\n{\n  \"filename\": \"API设计规范\",\n  \"content\": \"# API 设计规范\\n\\n## 概述\\n\\n本文档定义了 REST API 的设计标准。\"\n}\n```\n\n## 注意事项\n\n- 知识库 space_id: `7615846908665285857`\n- 需要在飞书开放平台开通 `wiki:space:readonly` 和 `wiki:node:create` 权限\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776780355941}}
{"type":"message","id":"2ff30646","parentId":"21adaffb","timestamp":"2026-04-21T14:08:14.954Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me write the comprehensive architecture document in Markdown format. I have all the information I need from:\n1. The source code (run_agent.py, hermes_state.py, model_tools.py, tools/registry.py, toolsets.py, agent/context_compressor.py, agent/prompt_builder.py)\n2. Official documentation (agent loop, tools runtime, provider runtime, gateway internals, session storage, context compression)\n3. File structure of the repo\n\nLet me create a comprehensive document with mermaid diagrams.","thinkingSignature":"98e827a1ce6b2396ad5748cf138a2d2973cd0bbe31dd45f396ff76d3d2a65582"},{"type":"text","text":"现在我来编写完整的架构文档并写入飞书知识库。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_function_oq4iv1ns11jw_1","name":"feishu_create_doc","arguments":{"markdown":"# Hermes Agent 技术架构深度解读\n\n> 文档版本：v1.0 | 基于：NousResearch/hermes-agent @ main | 更新：2026-04-21\n\n---\n\n## 一、项目概览\n\nHermes Agent 是一个开源的 **AI 编程助手 / Agent 运行时**，由 NousResearch 开发。其核心设计目标是为大语言模型提供一套完整的工具调用执行框架，使其能够自主完成复杂的多步骤任务。\n\n**核心特性：**\n\n- 🔧 **30+ 内置工具**：Web 搜索、文件操作、终端执行、浏览器自动化、代码执行、子任务委托等\n- 🌍 **14+ 消息平台集成**：Telegram、Discord、Slack、WhatsApp、飞书、微信企业版、Signal、Matrix 等\n- 🧠 **持久化记忆**：跨会话的 SQLite 会话存储 + FTS5 全文搜索\n- 💾 **上下文压缩**：双层压缩系统（50% 阈值内压缩 + 85% 网关安全网）\n- 🔄 **多 API 模式**：OpenAI Chat Completions、Anthropic Messages API、OpenAI Responses/Codex API\n- 🔌 **插件系统**：支持工具插件、上下文引擎插件、内存提供程序插件\n- 🛡️ **安全防护**：提示词注入检测、危险命令审批流、环境隔离执行\n\n---\n\n## 二、整体架构图\n\n```mermaid\nflowchart TB\n    subgraph Input[\"📥 输入层\"]\n        CLI[\"CLI 交互<br/>(hermes chat)\"]\n        Gateway[\"消息网关 Gateway<br/>(14+ 消息平台)\"]\n        API[\"API 服务器<br/>(hermes-api-server)\"]\n        ACP[\"Editor 插件集成<br/>(ACP)\"]\n        Cron[\"定时任务 Cron<br/>(hermes cron)\"]\n    end\n\n    subgraph Core[\"🔥 核心引擎层\"]\n        AIAgent[\"AIAgent<br/>(run_agent.py · 12K行)\"]\n        PromptBuilder[\"PromptBuilder<br/>(系统提示构建)\"]\n        ContextEngine[\"ContextEngine<br/>(上下文压缩引擎)\"]\n        MemoryManager[\"MemoryManager<br/>(记忆管理)\"]\n    end\n\n    subgraph ToolLayer[\"🛠️ 工具层\"]\n        Registry[\"ToolRegistry<br/>(自注册工具中心)\"]\n        Toolsets[\"Toolsets<br/>(工具集系统)\"]\n        MCP[\"MCP 工具<br/>(外部服务器)\"]\n        Plugins[\"插件工具<br/>(用户扩展)\"]\n    end\n\n    subgraph Tools[\"📦 内置工具集\"]\n        subgraph CoreTools[\"核心工具\"]\n            Terminal[\"terminal<br/>process\"]\n            Files[\"read_file<br/>write_file<br/>patch<br/>search_files\"]\n            Web[\"web_search<br/>web_extract\"]\n            Browser[\"browser_navigate<br/>browser_snapshot<br/>browser_*\"]\n        end\n        subgraph CognitiveTools[\"认知工具\"]\n            Vision[\"vision_analyze\"]\n            TTS[\"text_to_speech\"]\n            Skills[\"skills_list<br/>skill_view<br/>skill_manage\"]\n        end\n        subgraph ControlTools[\"控制工具\"]\n            Todo[\"todo\"]\n            Memory[\"memory\"]\n            SessionSearch[\"session_search\"]\n            Delegate[\"delegate_task\"]\n            CronJob[\"cronjob\"]\n            Clarify[\"clarify\"]\n        end\n    end\n\n    subgraph LLM[\"🤖 LLM 适配层\"]\n        subgraph Adapters[\"API 适配器\"]\n            OpenAI[\"OpenAI<br/>Chat Completions\"]\n            Anthropic[\"Anthropic<br/>Messages API\"]\n            Codex[\"OpenAI Codex<br/>Responses API\"]\n            Bedrock[\"Bedrock<br/>Adapter\"]\n            Gemini[\"Gemini<br/>Native\"]\n        end\n        ProviderResolver[\"ProviderResolver<br/>(运行时解析)\")\n        FallbackMgr[\"FallbackMgr<br/>(降级管理)\"]\n    end\n\n    subgraph Storage[\"💾 持久化层\"]\n        SessionDB[\"SessionDB<br/>(SQLite + WAL + FTS5)\"]\n        EnvConfig[\"环境配置<br/>(~/.hermes/.env)\"]\n        YamlConfig[\"YamlConfig<br/>(config.yaml)\"]\n        MemoryFiles[\"Memory Files<br/>(MEMORY.md / USER.md)\"]\n    end\n\n    subgraph Runtime[\"⚙️ 运行时\"]\n        Env[\"TerminalEnv<br/>DockerEnv<br/>SSHEnv\"]\n        Approval[\"危险命令审批<br/>(approval.py)\"]\n        Interrupts[\"中断处理<br/>(interrupt.py)\"]\n        Compression[\"上下文压缩<br/>(context_compressor.py)\"]\n    end\n\n    Input --> Core\n    CLI --> AIAgent\n    Gateway --> AIAgent\n    API --> AIAgent\n    ACP --> AIAgent\n    Cron --> AIAgent\n\n    AIAgent --> PromptBuilder\n    AIAgent --> ContextEngine\n    AIAgent --> MemoryManager\n    AIAgent --> ToolLayer\n\n    Registry --> Toolsets\n    Toolsets --> CoreTools\n    Toolsets --> CognitiveTools\n    Toolsets --> ControlTools\n    MCP --> Registry\n    Plugins --> Registry\n\n    ProviderResolver --> OpenAI\n    ProviderResolver --> Anthropic\n    ProviderResolver --> Codex\n    ProviderResolver --> FallbackMgr\n    ProviderResolver --> Bedrock\n    ProviderResolver --> Gemini\n\n    AIAgent --> Storage\n    AIAgent --> Runtime\n    AIAgent --> LLM\n```\n\n---\n\n## 三、核心模块详解\n\n### 3.1 AIAgent — 核心智能体引擎\n\n**文件位置：** `run_agent.py`（约 12,000 行）\n\nAIAgent 是整个系统的中枢神经，负责：\n\n1. **提示词组装** — 调用 `PromptBuilder` 合成系统提示词\n2. **API 模式解析** — 自动识别 chat_completions / anthropic_messages / codex_responses\n3. **可中断 API 调用** — 后台线程执行 HTTP 请求，主线程监听中断事件\n4. **工具调用循环** — 单工具顺序执行，多工具并发（ThreadPoolExecutor）\n5. **会话历史维护** — OpenAI 格式消息队列\n6. **压缩 & 回退** — 上下文超限时触发压缩，API 失败时切换备用模型\n\n#### 3.1.1 三大 API 执行模式\n\n```mermaid\nflowchart LR\n    subgraph Resolution[\"模式解析优先级\"]\n        P1[\"显式 api_mode 参数<br/>最高优先级\"]\n        P2[\"Provider 检测<br/>(e.g. anthropic)\"]\n        P3[\"Base URL 启发式<br/>(e.g. api.anthropic.com)\"]\n        P4[\"默认: chat_completions\"]\n    end\n\n    P1 --> Mode\n    P2 --> Mode\n    P3 --> Mode\n    P4 --> Mode\n\n    subgraph Mode[\"三种 API 模式\"]\n        direction TB\n        CC[\"chat_completions<br/>OpenAI 兼容端点<br/>openai.OpenAI 客户端\"]\n        AM[\"anthropic_messages<br/>原生 Anthropic<br/>anthropic.Anthropic 适配器\"]\n        CR[\"codex_responses<br/>OpenAI Responses API<br/>Codex 格式\"]\n    end\n```\n\n**消息格式统一抽象：** 所有消息最终转换为 OpenAI 风格（role/content/tool_calls）进行内部处理。\n\n#### 3.1.2 Agent 循环生命周期\n\n```mermaid\nsequenceDiagram\n    participant User as 用户输入\n    participant Agent as AIAgent.run_conversation()\n    participant Prompt as PromptBuilder\n    participant LLM as LLM API\n    participant Registry as ToolRegistry\n    participant Tools as 工具处理器\n    participant DB as SessionDB\n\n    User->>Agent: run_conversation(user_message)\n    Agent->>Agent: 生成 task_id\n    Agent->>Agent: 追加用户消息到历史\n    Agent->>Prompt: build_system_prompt()\n    Prompt->>Agent: 组装好的系统提示词\n\n    alt 上下文超50%?\n        Agent->>Agent: 触发 ContextCompressor\n    end\n\n    loop Tool Call Loop (最多90轮)\n        Agent->>Agent: 构建 API 消息格式\n        Agent->>Agent: 注入临时提示层\n        Agent->>LLM: _api_call_with_interrupt()\n        LLM-->>Agent: 响应\n\n        alt 有 tool_calls\n            Agent->>Registry: dispatch(tool_name, args)\n            Registry->>Tools: 执行工具\n            Tools-->>Agent: JSON 结果\n            Agent->>Agent: 追加 tool 消息到历史\n\n        else 纯文本响应\n            Agent->>DB: append_message()\n            Agent->>DB: update_token_counts()\n            Agent->>DB: end_session()\n            Agent-->>User: final_response\n            break 循环结束\n        end\n    end\n```\n\n#### 3.1.3 可中断 API 调用机制\n\n```mermaid\nflowchart TB\n    subgraph Main[\"主线程\"]\n        M1[\"发起 API 调用请求\"]\n        M2[\"等待响应 / 中断事件 / 超时\"]\n    end\n\n    subgraph Background[\"后台线程\"]\n        B1[\"执行 HTTP POST 请求\"]\n        B2[\"响应就绪 / 超时\"]\n    end\n\n    subgraph Events[\"中断触发事件\"]\n        E1[\"用户发送新消息\"]\n        E2[\"用户输入 /stop\"]\n        E3[\"收到系统信号\"]\n    end\n\n    M1 -->|\"传递给后台线程\"| B1\n    B1 --> M2\n    E1 -->|\"设置中断标志\"| M2\n    E2 -->|\"设置中断标志\"| M2\n    E3 -->|\"设置中断标志\"| M2\n\n    M2 -->|\"API 线程被放弃<br/>响应被丢弃\"| Done[\"干净退出\"]\n```\n\n**关键点：** API 线程被放弃时，响应不注入历史记录，保证对话状态一致性。\n\n#### 3.1.4 迭代预算与降级\n\n```mermaid\nflowchart TB\n    subgraph Budget[\"迭代预算\"]\n        B1[\"默认最大 90 轮\"]\n        B2[\"子代理独立预算<br/>(默认 50 轮)\"]\n        B3[\"父+子代总轮数<br/>可超过父级上限\"]\n    end\n\n    subgraph Fallback[\"模型降级流程\"]\n        F1[\"API 错误检测<br/>(429 / 5xx / 401 / 403)\"]\n        F2[\"检查 fallback_providers 列表\"]\n        F3[\"按顺序尝试备用模型\"]\n        F4[\"成功 → 继续对话\"]\n        F5[\"401/403 → 尝试刷新凭证\"]\n        F6[\"失败 → 报告错误\"]\n    end\n\n    B1 --> F1\n    F1 --> F2\n    F2 --> F3\n    F3 --> F4\n    F4 --> Done1[\"继续运行\"]\n    F3 --> F5\n    F5 --> F6\n    F6 --> Done2[\"终止并返回\"]\n```\n\n---\n\n### 3.2 工具系统 — 自注册 + 工具集编排\n\n**核心文件：**\n\n- `tools/registry.py` — 工具注册中心\n- `model_tools.py` — 工具编排层\n- `toolsets.py` — 工具集定义\n\n#### 3.2.1 工具注册模型\n\n```mermaid\nflowchart TB\n    subgraph Registration[\"注册阶段（导入时）\"]\n        TM1[\"tools/*.py<br/>每个工具模块\"]\n        TM2[\"registry.register(<br/>name, toolset, schema,<br/>handler, check_fn, ...)\"]\n        TM3[\"ToolEntry 存入<br/>ToolRegistry._tools\"]\n    end\n\n    subgraph Discovery[\"发现阶段\"]\n        D1[\"discover_builtin_tools()<br/>(AST 扫描)\"]\n        D2[\"过滤 __init__.py<br/>registry.py, mcp_tool.py\"]\n        D3[\"仅导入含顶层<br/>registry.register() 的模块\"]\n    end\n\n    subgraph Query[\"查询阶段\"]\n        Q1[\"get_tool_definitions()<br/>(enabled/disabled toolsets)\"]\n        Q2[\"check_fn() 过滤可用性\"]\n        Q3[\"返回 OpenAI 格式<br/>tool schemas\"]\n    end\n\n    TM1 --> D1\n    D1 --> D2\n    D2 --> D3\n    D3 --> TM2\n    TM2 --> TM3\n    Q1 --> Q2\n    Q2 --> Q3\n```\n\n**自注册设计要点：**\n\n- 新增工具只需在 `tools/` 下创建 `.py` 文件，模块顶层调用 `register()` 即可\n- AST 扫描确保仅导入真正注册工具的模块，避免辅助函数模块被误导入\n- `check_fn` 运行时检查（如 API Key 是否存在），不可用工具自动过滤\n- MCP 工具和插件工具通过相同路径注入\n\n#### 3.2.2 工具分发流程\n\n```mermaid\nsequenceDiagram\n    participant LLM as 大语言模型\n    participant Agent as AIAgent\n    participant Hooks as Plugin Hooks\n    participant Registry as ToolRegistry\n    participant Tool as 工具处理器\n\n    LLM-->>Agent: tool_call: {name, arguments}\n    Agent->>Agent: coerce_tool_args()<br/>(类型强制转换)\n    Agent->>Hooks: pre_tool_call 钩子\n    Hooks-->>Agent: block_message?\n\n    alt 被插件拦截\n        Agent-->>LLM: 返回 block 错误\n    else 放行\n        Agent->>Registry: dispatch(name, args)\n        Registry->>Registry: lookup ToolEntry\n        alt 同步处理\n            Registry->>Tool: 直接调用\n        else 异步处理\n            Registry->>Tool: _run_async()<br/>(持久事件循环桥接)\n        end\n        Tool-->>Registry: result JSON\n        Registry-->>Agent: result JSON\n        Agent->>Hooks: post_tool_call 钩子\n        Agent->>Hooks: transform_tool_result 钩子\n        Agent->>Agent: 追加 tool 消息到历史\n        Agent->>LLM: 继续循环\n    end\n```\n\n#### 3.2.3 工具集层级关系\n\n```mermaid\nflowchart TB\n    subgraph 平台工具集\n        HCLI[\"hermes-cli\"]\n        HTG[\"hermes-telegram\"]\n        HD[\"hermes-discord\"]\n        HFE[\"hermes-feishu\"]\n        HWA[\"hermes-whatsapp\"]\n        HG[\"hermes-gateway<br/>(所有平台并集)\"]\n    end\n\n    subgraph 场景工具集\n        SAFE[\"safe<br/>(无终端访问)\"]\n        DEBUG[\"debugging<br/>(终端+文件+搜索)\"]\n        ACP[\"hermes-acp<br/>(编辑器集成)\"]\n    end\n\n    subgraph 原子工具集\n        WEB[\"web\"]\n        FILE[\"file\"]\n        BROWSER[\"browser\"]\n        TERMINAL[\"terminal\"]\n        VISION[\"vision\"]\n        MEMORY[\"memory\"]\n        TTS[\"tts\"]\n    end\n\n    HG --> HCLI\n    HG --> HTG\n    HG --> HD\n    HG --> HFE\n    HG --> HWA\n    HCLI --> SAFE\n    HCLI --> DEBUG\n    ACP --> SAFE\n    SAFE --> WEB\n    SAFE --> VISION\n    DEBUG --> WEB\n    DEBUG --> FILE\n    DEBUG --> TERMINAL\n```\n\n**工具集 resolution 算法：**\n\n1. 支持直接指定工具名或工具集名\n2. 工具集可引用其他工具集（`includes` 字段），支持钻石依赖\n3. 循环引用检测 — 静默跳过，防止死循环\n4. 特殊名称 `all` / `*` 解析为所有可用工具\n\n#### 3.2.4 危险命令审批流\n\n```mermaid\nflowchart TB\n    C[\"命令执行\"] --> Check[\"检测危险模式\"]\n    Check --> Match{\"匹配到<br/>DANGEROUS_PATTERNS?\"}\n\n    Match -->|否| Safe[\"直接执行\"]\n    Match -->|是| Approval\n\n    subgraph Approval[\"交互式审批\"]\n        A1{\"平台\"}\n        A2[\"CLI 模式<br/>交互式提示\"]\n        A3[\"Gateway 模式<br/>异步审批回调\"]\n        A4[\"智能审批<br/>(LLM 自动判断)\"]\n        A5[\"永久白名单<br/>(写入 config.yaml)\"]\n    end\n\n    A1 -->|CLI| A2\n    A1 -->|Gateway| A3\n    A2 --> A4\n    A3 --> A4\n    A4 -->|\"低风险\"| Safe\n    A4 -->|\"高风险\"| Block[\"拒绝执行\"]\n    A4 -->|\"allow permanent\"| A5\n\n    A5 --> Safe\n```\n\n**危险模式覆盖：** 递归删除(`rm -rf`)、格式化磁盘(`mkfs/dd`)、SQL破坏操作、系统配置覆写、服务操控、远程代码执行(`curl|sh`)、Fork炸弹等。\n\n---\n\n### 3.3 会话存储 — SQLite WAL + FTS5\n\n**文件位置：** `hermes_state.py`\n\n```mermaid\nflowchart TB\n    subgraph DB[\"~/.hermes/state.db (SQLite WAL)\"]\n        subgraph Tables[\"核心表\"]\n            Sessions[\"sessions 表<br/>元数据+Token统计+计费\"]\n            Messages[\"messages 表<br/>完整消息历史\"]\n            FTS[\"messages_fts 虚拟表<br/>(FTS5 全文搜索)\"]\n            Ver[\"schema_version 表<br/>(迁移状态)\"]\n        end\n\n        subgraph Indexes[\"索引\"]\n            Idx1[\"idx_sessions_source\"]\n            Idx2[\"idx_sessions_parent\"]\n            Idx3[\"idx_sessions_started\"]\n            Idx4[\"idx_sessions_title_unique\"]\n            Idx5[\"idx_messages_session\"]\n        end\n    end\n\n    subgraph Features[\"关键特性\"]\n        F1[\"WAL 模式<br/>(并发读+单写)\"]\n        F2[\"应用层随机退避重试<br/>(20-150ms jitter)\"]\n        F3[\"FTS5 触发器同步<br/>(INSERT/UPDATE/DELETE)\"]\n        F4[\"会话标题唯一性约束\"]\n        F5[\"压缩链向前投影\"]\n        F6[\"CJK LIKE 回退搜索\"]\n    end\n```\n\n#### 3.3.1 写竞争处理策略\n\n```mermaid\nflowchart LR\n    subgraph Problem[\"问题背景\"]\n        P1[\"多进程共享 state.db<br/>(Gateway + CLI + Worktree)\"]\n        P2[\"SQLite 默认30s超时<br/>→  convoy effect\"]\n    end\n\n    subgraph Solution[\"Hermes 的解决\"]\n        S1[\"超时设为 1 秒<br/>(短超时)\"]\n        S2[\"应用层随机退避<br/>(20-150ms jitter, 最多15次)\"]\n        S3[\"BEGIN IMMEDIATE<br/>(事务开始即抢锁)\"]\n        S4[\"每50次写操作<br/>PASSIVE WAL checkpoint\"]\n    end\n\n    P1 --> Problem\n    S1 --> Solution\n    S2 --> Solution\n    S3 --> Solution\n    S4 --> Solution\n```\n\n#### 3.3.2 会话血缘（Lineage）追踪\n\n```mermaid\nflowchart TB\n    subgraph Lineage[\"压缩触发的会话分裂\"]\n        S1[\"原始会话<br/>end_reason='compression'\"]\n        S2[\"子会话<br/>(parent_session_id → S1)\"]\n        S3[\"压缩链投影<br/>(list_sessions_rich)<br/>自动显示最新会话\"]\n    end\n\n    subgraph TitleSystem[\"标题系统\"]\n        T1[\"会话可设置唯一标题\"]\n        T2[\"自动生成连续编号<br/>(title → title #2 → title #3)\"]\n        T3[\"按标题解析会话 ID<br/>(支持 #N 后缀)\"]\n    end\n\n    subgraph Search[\"搜索能力\"]\n        SR1[\"FTS5 全文搜索<br/>(snippet 高亮)\"]\n        SR2[\"来源过滤<br/>(cli / telegram / discord)\"]\n        SR3[\"角色过滤<br/>(user / assistant / tool)\"]\n        SR4[\"上下文感知<br/>(返回匹配前后各1条消息)\"]\n    end\n```\n\n---\n\n### 3.4 上下文压缩 — 双层压缩系统\n\n```mermaid\nflowchart TB\n    subgraph Layer1[\"第一层：网关会话卫生 (85% 阈值)\"]\n        L1A[\"位于 gateway/run.py\"]\n        L1B[\"会话增长的安全网<br/>(防止隔夜积累)\"]\n        L1C[\"粗略字符估算<br/>(fallback)\"]\n        L1D[\"仅在 history ≥ 4 时触发\"]\n    end\n\n    subgraph Layer2[\"第二层：Agent ContextCompressor (50% 阈值)\"]\n        L2A[\"位于 agent/context_compressor.py\"]\n        L2B[\"精确 API Token 计数\"]\n        L2C[\"可插拔 ContextEngine 接口\"]\n        L2D[\"可配置：threshold / target_ratio / protect_last_n\"]\n    end\n\n    subgraph Algorithm[\"压缩算法（4阶段）\"]\n        A1[\"阶段1：修剪旧工具结果<br/>(>200字符 → 占位符)\"]\n        A2[\"阶段2：确定边界<br/>(保护前3条+尾部20条)\"]\n        A3[\"阶段3：LLM 生成结构化摘要\"]\n        A4[\"阶段4：组装压缩消息\"]\n    end\n\n    Layer1 -->|\"超出85%仍触发\"| Layer2\n    Layer2 --> Algorithm\n```\n\n#### 压缩摘要结构模板\n\n```\n## Goal\n[用户想要完成的目标]\n\n## Constraints & Preferences\n[用户偏好、编码风格、约束条件、重要决策]\n\n## Progress\n### Done\n[已完成工作 — 文件路径、运行的命令、结果]\n\n### In Progress\n[正在进行的工作]\n\n### Blocked\n[遇到的障碍或问题]\n\n## Key Decisions\n[重要的技术决策及其原因]\n\n## Relevant Files\n[读取/修改/创建的文件 — 附简要说明]\n\n## Next Steps\n[接下来需要做什么]\n\n## Critical Context\n[具体值、错误消息、配置细节]\n```\n\n---\n\n### 3.5 消息网关（Gateway）\n\n**文件位置：** `gateway/run.py`（约 9,000 行）\n\nGateway 是 Hermes 的长驻进程，将 AI 助手连接到 14+ 消息平台。\n\n```mermaid\nflowchart TB\n    subgraph Gateway[\"GatewayRunner\"]\n        subgraph Adapters[\"14+ 平台适配器\"]\n            T[\"Telegram\"]\n            D[\"Discord\"]\n            S[\"Slack\"]\n            W[\"WhatsApp\"]\n            F[\"飞书/Lark\"]\n            Si[\"Signal\"]\n            Mx[\"Matrix\"]\n            M[\"Mattermost\"]\n            H[\"Home Assistant\"]\n            E[\"Email (IMAP/SMTP)\"]\n            SMS[\"SMS (Twilio)\"]\n            DT[\"钉钉\"]\n            WX[\"微信\"]\n            QQ[\"QQ\"]\n            WC[\"企业微信\"]\n        end\n\n        subgraph Core[\"网关核心\"]\n            MsgHandler[\"消息处理器<br/>_handle_message()\"]\n            SlashCmd[\"斜杠命令分发\"]\n            SessionGuard[\"两层运行守护<br/>(BaseAdapter + Runner)\"]\n            Pairing[\"DM 配对授权\"]\n        end\n\n        subgraph Persistence[\"会话管理\"]\n            SessionStore[\"SessionStore<br/>(SQLite 会话持久化)\"]\n            Delivery[\"Outbound 投递<br/>(delivery.py)\"]\n            Hooks[\"生命周期钩子\"]\n        end\n    end\n\n    Adapters --> MsgHandler\n    MsgHandler --> SlashCmd\n    MsgHandler --> SessionGuard\n    MsgHandler --> SessionStore\n    SessionStore --> Delivery\n    MsgHandler --> Hooks\n    Pairing --> SessionGuard\n```\n\n#### 3.5.1 双层消息守护机制\n\n```mermaid\nsequenceDiagram\n    participant User as 用户\n    participant Adapter as BaseAdapter\n    participant Runner as GatewayRunner\n    participant Agent as AIAgent\n\n    User->>Adapter: 新消息\n\n    Note over Adapter: Level 1 Guard\n    alt Agent 正在运行\n        Adapter->>Adapter: 队列消息\n        Adapter->>Adapter: 设置中断事件\n    else Agent 空闲\n        Adapter->>Runner: 转发消息\n    end\n\n    Note over Runner: Level 2 Guard\n    alt /stop /new /approve /deny\n        Runner->>Runner: 内联分发（跳过运行守护）\n    else 普通消息 + Agent 运行中\n        Runner->>Agent: interrupt()\n    else 普通消息 + Agent 空闲\n        Runner->>Runner: 创建 AIAgent\n        Runner->>Agent: run_conversation()\n    end\n```\n\n#### 3.5.2 生命周期钩子系统\n\n```mermaid\nflowchart TB\n    subgraph Hooks[\"Gateway 钩子事件\"]\n        E1[\"gateway:startup<br/>网关进程启动\"]\n        E2[\"session:start<br/>新会话开始\"]\n        E3[\"session:end<br/>会话结束\"]\n        E4[\"session:reset<br/>(/new)\"]\n        E5[\"agent:start<br/>Agent 开始处理\"]\n        E6[\"agent:step<br/>单轮工具迭代完成\"]\n        E7[\"agent:end<br/>Agent 返回响应\"]\n        E8[\"command:*<br/>任意斜杠命令\"]\n    end\n\n    subgraph Sources[\"钩子来源\"]\n        B[\"gateway/builtin_hooks/<br/>(始终激活)\"]\n        U[\"~/.hermes/hooks/<br/>(用户安装)\"]\n    end\n\n    subgraph Usage[\"用途\"]\n        U1[\"系统提示注入<br/>(BOOT.md)\"]\n        U2[\"会话行为定制\"]\n        U3[\"数据同步\"]\n        U4[\"通知推送\"]\n    end\n\n    B --> Hooks\n    U --> Hooks\n    Hooks --> U1\n    Hooks --> U2\n    Hooks --> U3\n    Hooks --> U4\n```\n\n---\n\n### 3.6 提示词构建系统\n\n**文件位置：** `agent/prompt_builder.py`\n\n```mermaid\nflowchart TB\n    subgraph Input[\"输入源\"]\n        I1[\"workspace/AGENTS.md\"]\n        I2[\"workspace/SOUL.md<br/>(人格设定)\"]\n        I3[\"workspace/IDENTITY.md\"]\n        I4[\"workspace/USER.md\"]\n        I5[\"skills/ 目录<br/>(技能文档)\"]\n        I6[\".cursorrules<br/>(项目规则)\"]\n        I7[\"MEMORY.md<br/>(长期记忆)\"]\n    end\n\n    subgraph Injection[\"注入层\"]\n        Inj1[\"内存上下文块<br/>(build_memory_context_block)\"]\n        Inj2[\"技能引导<br/>(SKILLS_GUIDANCE)\"]\n        Inj3[\"会话搜索引导<br/>(SESSION_SEARCH_GUIDANCE)\"]\n        Inj4[\"平台提示<br/>(PLATFORM_HINTS)\"]\n        Inj5[\"NOUS 订阅提示<br/>(build_nous_subscription_prompt)\"]\n    end\n\n    subgraph Security[\"安全扫描\"]\n        S1[\"_CONTEXT_THREAT_PATTERNS<br/>(10+ 种注入模式)\"]\n        S2[\"不可见 Unicode 检测<br/>(U+200B 等零宽字符)\"]\n        S3[\"HTML 隐匿注入检测\"]\n        S4[\"危险 curl 命令检测\"]\n        S5[\"发现威胁 → 阻止加载\"]\n    end\n\n    subgraph Output[\"输出\"]\n        O[\"最终系统提示词<br/>(注入 AIAgent)\"]\n    end\n\n    Input --> Security\n    Security -->|\"通过\"| Input\n    Security -->|\"阻止加载\"| Blocked[\"[BLOCKED: ...]\")\n    Input --> Injection\n    Injection --> O\n```\n\n---\n\n### 3.7 提供商运行时解析\n\n**文件位置：** `hermes_cli/runtime_provider.py`、`hermes_cli/auth.py`\n\n```mermaid\nflowchart TB\n    subgraph Resolution[\"解析优先级\"]\n        P1[\"显式 CLI 参数\"]\n        P2[\"config.yaml 配置\"]\n        P3[\"环境变量\"]\n        P4[\"Provider 默认值\"]\n    end\n\n    subgraph Providers[\"支持的 Provider 家族\"]\n        OAI[\"OpenAI 原生\"]\n        OR[\"OpenRouter\"]\n        AN[\"Anthropic 原生<br/>(Messages API)\"]\n        GG[\"Google/Gemini\"]\n        DS[\"DeepSeek\"]\n        OX[\"OpenCode Zen/Go\"]\n        K[\"Kimi/Moonshot\"]\n        MX[\"MiniMax\"]\n        HC[\"HuggingFace\"]\n        Custom[\"自定义 OpenAI<br/>兼容端点\"]\n        Nous[\"Nous Portal\"]\n        AIG[\"AI Gateway (Vercel)\"]\n    end\n\n    subgraph Output[\"输出\"]\n        Out1[\"provider 名称\"]\n        Out2[\"api_mode\"]\n        Out3[\"base_url\"]\n        Out4[\"api_key\"]\n        Out5[\"source (来源标识)\"]\n    end\n\n    Resolution --> Providers\n    Providers --> Output\n```\n\n**密钥隔离策略：** 每个 Provider 的 API Key 仅发送到其对应的 Base URL，避免跨端点泄露（如 OPENROUTER_API_KEY 只能发往 openrouter.ai）。\n\n---\n\n### 3.8 插件系统\n\n```mermaid\nflowchart TB\n    subgraph PluginTypes[\"插件类型\"]\n        PT1[\"工具插件<br/>(注册额外工具)\"]\n        PT2[\"上下文引擎插件<br/>(替代 ContextCompressor)\"]\n        PT3[\"内存提供程序插件<br/>(如 Honcho)\"]\n        PT4[\"Gateway 钩子插件<br/>(生命周期扩展)\"]\n    end\n\n    subgraph Discovery[\"发现路径\"]\n        D1[\"~/.hermes/plugins/\"]\n        D2[\"项目 plugins/ 目录\"]\n        D3[\"pip 安装的插件\"]\n    end\n\n    subgraph Lifecycle[\"钩子生命周期\"]\n        HL1[\"pre_tool_call — 执行前拦截\"]\n        HL2[\"post_tool_call — 执行后观察\"]\n        HL3[\"transform_tool_result — 结果转换\"]\n        HL4[\"session:start/end — 会话事件\"]\n    end\n\n    PT1 --> PluginTypes\n    PT2 --> PluginTypes\n    PT3 --> PluginTypes\n    PT4 --> PluginTypes\n    D1 --> Discovery\n    D2 --> Discovery\n    D3 --> Discovery\n    Discovery --> Lifecycle\n```\n\n---\n\n## 四、目录结构全景\n\n```\nhermes-agent/\n├── run_agent.py          # 🔥 AIAgent 核心引擎 (~12K 行)\n├── cli.py                # CLI 入口 (~10K 行)\n├── hermes_state.py       # SQLite 会话存储\n├── model_tools.py        # 工具编排层\n├── toolsets.py           # 工具集定义\n│\n├── agent/                # Agent 核心模块\n│   ├── prompt_builder.py        # 系统提示词构建\n│   ├── context_compressor.py    # 上下文压缩\n│   ├── context_engine.py        # ContextEngine ABC（可插拔）\n│   ├── auxiliary_client.py      # 辅助 LLM 客户端\n│   ├── prompt_caching.py        # Anthropic 提示缓存\n│   ├── anthropic_adapter.py    # Anthropic 适配器\n│   ├── model_metadata.py        # 模型元数据缓存\n│   ├── memory_manager.py        # 记忆管理器\n│   ├── subdirectory_hints.py    # 子目录提示追踪\n│   ├── error_classifier.py      # API 错误分类\n│   ├── retry_utils.py           # 重试工具\n│   └── codex_responses_adapter.py  # Codex Responses 适配器\n│\n├── tools/                # 工具实现\n│   ├── registry.py               # 工具注册中心\n│   ├── terminal_tool.py          # 终端执行\n│   ├── file_tools.py             # 文件读写搜索\n│   ├── web_search_tool.py        # Web 搜索\n│   ├── web_extract_tool.py       # Web 内容提取\n│   ├── browser_tool.py           # 浏览器自动化\n│   ├── vision_tool.py            # 图像分析\n│   ├── image_generation_tool.py  # 图像生成\n│   ├── code_execution_tool.py    # 代码沙箱执行\n│   ├── delegate_tool.py          # 子任务委托\n│   ├── todo_tool.py              # 任务规划\n│   ├── memory_tool.py            # 持久记忆\n│   ├── session_search_tool.py    # 会话搜索\n│   ├── cronjob_tool.py           # 定时任务\n│   ├── text_to_speech_tool.py    # 语音合成\n│   ├── mcp_tool.py               # MCP 工具桥接\n│   ├── approval.py              # 危险命令审批\n│   ├── environments/            # 终端执行环境\n│   │   ├── local.py\n│   │   ├── docker.py\n│   │   ├── ssh.py\n│   │   └── ...\n│   └── ...\n│\n├── gateway/              # 消息网关\n│   ├── run.py            # GatewayRunner 主循环 (~9K 行)\n│   ├── session.py        # 会话存储\n│   ├── delivery.py       # 出站消息投递\n│   ├── pairing.py        # DM 配对授权\n│   ├── hooks.py          # 钩子系统\n│   ├── mirror.py         # 跨会话消息镜像\n│   ├── builtin_hooks/    # 内置钩子\n│   └── platforms/       # 平台适配器\n│       ├── base.py               # BaseAdapter 基类\n│       ├── telegram.py\n│       ├── discord.py\n│       ├── slack.py\n│       ├── whatsapp.py\n│       ├── feishu.py             # 飞书适配器\n│       ├── signal.py\n│       ├── matrix.py\n│       ├── mattermost.py\n│       ├── homeassistant.py\n│       ├── email.py\n│       ├── sms.py\n│       ├── dingtalk.py\n│       ├── wecom.py\n│       ├── weixin.py\n│       ├── qqbot/\n│       ├── webhook.py\n│       ├── api_server.py\n│       └── bluebubbles.py\n│\n├── hermes_cli/           # CLI 命令模块\n│   ├── main.py                  # CLI 主入口\n│   ├── config.py                # 配置管理\n│   ├── gateway.py               # Gateway CLI\n│   ├── models.py                # 模型配置\n│   ├── providers.py             # Provider 配置\n│   ├── cron.py                  # Cron CLI\n│   ├── plugins.py               # 插件系统\n│   ├── auth.py                  # 认证\n│   ├── doctor.py                # 诊断\n│   ├── commands.py              # 命令解析\n│   ├── runtime_provider.py      # 运行时解析\n│   ├── model_switch.py          # 模型切换\n│   ├── hooks.py                 # CLI 钩子\n│   └── ...\n│\n├── environments/         # RL/Agent 环境\n│   ├── agent_loop.py\n│   ├── hermes_swe_env/\n│   ├── agentic_opd_env.py\n│   └── ...\n│\n├── plugins/              # 用户插件目录\n│   ├── memory/                   # 内存提供程序插件\n│   ├── disk-cleanup/\n│   └── ...\n│\n├── acp_adapter/          # ACP 编辑器集成\n├── acp_registry/\n├── cron/                 # Cron 作业\n├── web/                  # Web 服务\n├── ui-tui/               # TUI 界面\n├── tinker-atropos/       # RL 训练系统\n├── tests/\n└── skills/               # 技能目录（用户自定义）\n```\n\n---\n\n## 五、关键设计哲学\n\n### 5.1 消息格式统一抽象\n\n无论底层是 OpenAI Chat Completions、Anthropic Messages API 还是 OpenAI Responses API，所有消息最终在 AIAgent 内部统一转换为 OpenAI 风格格式。这种设计确保了上层逻辑（工具循环、压缩、历史管理）与底层 LLM 提供商解耦。\n\n### 5.2 工具自注册 + 零配置发现\n\n新增工具无需修改任何注册表或配置文件，只需在 `tools/` 下创建模块并调用 `registry.register()` 即可被自动发现。AST 扫描确保仅导入真正声明了工具的模块。\n\n### 5.3 可插拔架构\n\n关键抽象均支持替换：\n\n- **ContextEngine** — 默认 lossy summarization，可替换为 LCM（无损上下文管理）插件\n- **MemoryProvider** — 默认文件（MEMORY.md），可替换为 Honcho 等外部系统\n- **LLM Provider** — 通过统一 runtime_provider 解析，支持任意 OpenAI 兼容端点\n\n### 5.4 安全第一\n\n- **提示词注入扫描**：10+ 正则模式 + 零宽字符检测 + HTML 隐匿检测\n- **危险命令二次确认**：审批流支持 CLI 交互/Gateway 异步/智能 LLM 自动判断\n- **密钥隔离**：每个 Provider 的 Key 仅发送到其对应端点\n- **错误容错**：所有工具执行双层包装，保证模型总能收到合法 JSON\n\n### 5.5 并发与持久化的平衡\n\n- SQLite WAL 模式支持多进程并发读 + 单写\n- 应用层随机退避替代 SQLite 内置确定性重试，解决 convoy effect\n- 每 50 次写操作自动 PASSIVE checkpoint，防止 WAL 文件无限增长\n\n---\n\n## 六、关键文件速查表\n\n| 文件 | 行数 | 职责 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `run_agent.py` | ~12,000 | AIAgent 核心循环 |\n| `cli.py` | ~10,000 | CLI 主入口 |\n| `gateway/run.py` | ~9,000 | GatewayRunner 核心 |\n| `tools/registry.py` | ~500 | 工具注册中心 |\n| `model_tools.py` | ~600 | 工具编排 API |\n| `toolsets.py` | ~500 | 工具集定义系统 |\n| `hermes_state.py` | ~1,500 | SQLite 会话存储 |\n| `agent/prompt_builder.py` | ~1,000 | 系统提示构建 |\n| `agent/context_compressor.py` | ~1,200 | 上下文压缩 |\n| `agent/auxiliary_client.py` | ~300 | 辅助 LLM 调用 |\n\n---\n\n*文档由 🦐 虾仔儿 生成 | 数据来源：NousResearch/hermes-agent @ main 分支 + 官方文档*\n","title":"Hermes Agent 技术架构深度解读","wiki_space":"7615846908665285857"}}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-cn","model":"MiniMax-M2.5-highspeed","usage":{"input":48034,"output":8240,"cacheRead":37026,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":93300,"cost":{"input":0.0288204,"output":0.019776,"cacheRead":0.0022215599999999996,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.050817959999999995}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776780355950}}
